channel.title: Router
channel.description:
Hiya, I posted earlier this morning about my problem and only got flamed for it. Ok here I go, I went through the Ultimate Server Guide, downloaded Testscape etc, I have everything EXCEPT, I am unable to log into my Router.
I got the Default Gateway IP, I put it into the IE bar, and clicked "Go" but all I got back was "This page cannot be displayed."
I use a laptop, but it's not wireless, I have a Motorola high speed modem if that helps any...[br][size=1]Posted on: April 07, 2007, 07:44:35 PM[/size][hr]Um, any help please?[br][size=1]Posted on: April 07, 2007, 07:57:59 PM[/size][hr]Oops, that's a Webstar modem, not motorola, forgot I changed last month :|
Still waiting for some help[br][size=1]Posted on: April 07, 2007, 08:10:13 PM[/size][hr]Cmon guys, cant you just take one minute to help me?
